data.description: Dont sleep on this one! Incredible opportunity to get a four bedroom, three and a half bath home off River Road.  Minutes from the Toledo Zoo and Anthony Wayne Trail.  Character abounds in every room of this home.  Freshly painted.  Hardwood floors, high ceilings, crown molding.  Front door was recently purchased from The Toledo Zoo!  Kitchen has been updated with granite countertops, and tile floor. Unique open pantry. Sliding glass doors to private backyard with privacy fence and oversized garage. Full tiled bath in basement.  Master bathroom updated with soaking tub and walk in closet.
